cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper discusses privacy preservation in personalization systems, which involves data management, machine learning, and security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DB (Databases), as the paper proposes a mechanism for privacy preservation. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, since the paper discusses privacy, it could also be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
